data.description:
AVAILABLE UNFURNISHED. This spectacular newly remodeled home seamlessly blends elegance, convenience, and an ideal location in the sought-after Woodland Hills neighborhood. Boasting 4 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a two-car garage, and a generous grassy yard, the property exudes curb appeal. The open floor plan creates a perfect indoor-outdoor flow, with a pergola off the kitchen through oversized sliding doors ideal for entertaining and family gatherings. The kitchen is a highlight with high-end fixtures, custom cabinetry, quartz countertops, a farmhouse sink, hidden hood range, stainless steel appliances, island and dining area. The primary bedroom impresses with a spacious walk-in closet and a designer-style bathroom featuring a natural oak dual vanity, matte porcelain tile flooring, and a large shower with beautiful brass fixtures. The secondary bathroom is equally impressive, showcasing floor-to-ceiling Bianco Matte ceramic wall tile, acrylic countertops/sink, radiant wall-mounted light fixtures, and thoughtful design. Additional features include luxury vinyl waterproof plank flooring, a brand-new roof, upgraded electrical and plumbing, NEST thermostat, fresh paint, recessed lighting, manicured landscaping, and an oversized solid oak front door. To top it all off - top-rated schools, shopping and restaurants are all nearby. Don't miss this opportunity to call this meticulously reimagined home yours! The house is available unfurnished, the photos are with staged furniture.

Renter is responsible for all utilities. One year lease term. Small pets allowed, up to 2, with an additional $500 deposit per pet. Income to be 3x monthly rent or more. Good credit.
